data.description: Great historic cottage Castroville Tx, original wood floors and high ceilings, new ceramic tile shower in bathroom with a touch of classic, gas cooking,  fenced yard all around, original smoke house turned into laundry and storage, located near Koenig Park great walking trails and special events, near Medina River.  Enjoy small town living.
